commit_message:
Remove decorator "classproperty"

The same goal can be achieved using the buit-in decorators @classmethod
and @property:

    class WithProperty(object):

        @classmethod
        @property
        def class_property(cls):
             return True

Trivial-Fix

Change-Id: Ia551583e3ca3bc110dfcf90686e8e9d5a6116c87
